            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>博盛半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7712:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7712\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7712-TW</a>)06日12:53上漲9.5元，股價漲停報105.0元，委買99,000張，成交610張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為功率半導體元件。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>博盛半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7712:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7712\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7712-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌12.39%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌3.95%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-801 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-797 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-4 張</li> <li>融資增減：+346 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
