            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5432:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5432\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5432-TW</a>)06日12:54股價上漲10元，報151.0元，漲幅7.09%，成交229張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5432:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5432\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5432-TW</a>)所屬產業為綠能環保，主要業務為太陽能系統組件。LCD模組。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌6.62%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌3.95%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-6 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-5 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>融資增減：-6 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
